    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "@nventuro reminded me that we use the underscore prefix for `internal` functions such as `_mint` and `_burn` in `StandardToken` because we later expose them through non-prefixed `external` functions. It's not possible to change visibility so we have to have the underscore.\r\n\r\nFor consistency, all `internal` functions should have the underscore prefix.\r\n\r\ncc @elopio ",
